data.description: Welcome to this stunning property located within the Kingwood Estates golf community. This magnificent home offers a wealth of desirable features that will exceed your expectations. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a spacious living area that provides ample room for relaxation and entertainment.  The wood flooring and vaulted ceilings adds both warmth and elegance to the space.  The natural light pouring in through the patio doors and windows further accentuates the beauty of the room.  The kitchen boasts stainless steel appliances combining style and functionality.  Adding to the kitchen, is a charming breakfast nook that provides the perfect spot for that morning coffee. The large primary bedroom is a true retreat, featuring a sitting area where you can unwind with a good book.  It also offers convenient access to the screened-in sleeping porch.  The primary bathroom has been thoughtfully updated to create a luxurious experience.  There are two additional bedrooms on the main level that share a full bath.  Working from home is a breeze with the dedicated office space.  The full, finished basement is a fantastic bonus.  It features a bar area, perfect for hosting gatherings and enjoying drinks with friends.  The cozy fireplace is a wonderful addition and makes the perfect spot to relax during chilly evenings.  Convenience is further enhanced by the one-car garage located in the basement, providing additional storage for your boat or golf cart. A NEW roof and NEW main level HVAC add additional value to this one-of-a-kind property. Optional membership for golf, tennis and swimming is available.  $640,000 valid until 12/31/23.
